bug.short_desc: [regression] "Help / Report Bug or Enhancement..." lacks entries for Mylyn in supported Eclipse products

long_desc.thetext:
Normally I reported Mylyn issues via "Help / Report Bug or Enhancement..."
But today I found that if I select "Eclipse" from the "Open Source Community" section, there are not entries for Mylyn.
What is missing here? I would like to have that back.
